":"條gene係somatic chromosome 同sex chromosome係完全唔同結論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n條題目係咪應該講清楚"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T11:46:04.000Z","msg":"Yes <br />\n我就係諗緊呢樣野"},{"pid":"0c992779ef815fd6259934f4418eff9e5fbb4a5f","tid":2209062,"uid":18844,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8204dfb5a6251c930e0529758f5b56c1168d6d20","tid":2209062,"uid":246369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T11:14:01.000Z","msg":"題目冇講個gene 係sex linked<br />\n剩係俾咗個pedigree，應該點做好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇可能係出錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔該晒各位巴絲打<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P553EL8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP553EL8.png&h=3e613151&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T11:47:21.000Z","msg":"首先 red-green colour blindness 應該係 sex-linked, 呢個當係 common sense<br />\n唔記得 link X or Y, dominant/recessive 唔緊要<br />\n<br />\n母親無病, 老豆有病<br />\n男同女都會中, 亦都可以同時唔中, 機率50% &amp; 50%<br />\n<br />\n假設 dominant, 咁一係 link X, 一係 link Y<br />\n假設 X-linked dominant, 咁所有女都會有病, 但有一個女無病, 咁即係 not X-linked dominant<br />\n假設 Y-linked dominant, 咁所有仔都會有病, 但有一個仔無病, 咁即係 not Y-linked dominant<br />\n<br />\n答案呼之肉出, 係C<br />\n咁當然, 你可以唔用做MC技巧再思考落去<br />\n<br />\n咁唔係sex-linked dominant, 咁緊係sex-linked recessive呢?<br />\n假設 X-linked recessive<br />\n咁1就係 XB Xb (細Xb係病gene, recessive, 佢係carrier)<br />\n2 就係 Xb Y<br />\n(XB, Xb) x (Xb, Y)<br />\n先講女, 3就係 (XB,Xb) 無病但係 carrier, 5 就係 (Xb, Xb) 佢有病<br />\n4就係 XB, Y, 正常(無病gene), 6就係 Xb, Y 有病<br />\n<br />\n就咁睇落去, X-linked recessive 好似岩 logic<br />\n<br />\n咁有無可能係 Y-linked recessive呢? 呢個比較複雜? 呢到唔講啦<br />\n因為用 X-linked recessive 可以令到 (2) &amp; (3) 選項正確, 夠做答案了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n十年無掂呢啲bio, 9up, 有錯屌細力啲"},{"pid":"908a39a61bf0aea37d96b92d22f5a986236f309e","tid":2209062,"uid":1884