 (姐係carrier) 因為 5 有事, 姐係爸媽都有條Xb (因為兩條X分別由爸媽黎)<br />\n3 係XB Xb (姐係carrier) 因為佢冇事 有最少一條XB (由媽黎 因為爸只會俾到Xb佢) --&gt; (3)啱<br />\n4 係XB Y 因為佢係男 Y一定由爸黎 X一定由媽黎 佢冇事姐係拎到媽條XB<br />\n--&gt; (2)啱"},{"pid":"18cd6110fa5eaf53b14a106e6ac9e927b5aecf65","tid":2209062,"uid":262677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T18:34:42.000Z","msg":"bio好有趣，但bio啲題做到有陰影，周圍都係地雷<br />\n<br />\n試過問點解pancreatic duct塞咗個胰臟會消化咗，我答因為細胞膜係lipid，但標準答案係pancreatic juice入面有lipase<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n重有evolution長答用嘅字眼同標準答案有少少唔一樣又會扣分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"601584fdad35b1c8a670903778785ba9fcef5562","tid":2209062,"uid":287991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8204dfb5a6251c930e0529758f5b56c1168d6d20","tid":2209062,"uid":246369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T11:14:01.000Z","msg":"題目冇講個gene 係sex linked<br />\n剩係俾咗個pedigree，應該點做好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇可能係出錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔該晒各位巴絲打<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P553EL8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP553EL8.png&h=3e613151&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T15:14:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Su0jMsS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSu0jMsS.jpg&h=769eea94&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0cbd3d71a99abd42681fe930d4f83e1b409c99d1","tid":2209062,"uid":61876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb19da5083e262c5927965be251d17663408f730","tid":2209062,"uid":246369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd59fe62edfb119e966dafacc36fc3cd7e12e84f","tid":2209062,"uid":3775,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"201d16a5e7e229d7a2e3b9e9eeab25456c4f3318","tid":2209062,"uid":246369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime